Hands don't feel anything!
What answers does your group prepare for this challenge?
- In my lectures I often say that the increased reality is the seventh break in the interaction between man and machine.
I think the octave could well be adding touch sensations.
In the meantime, one of the most interesting tricks is the use of the second hand as a support for the image.
Record the touch perfectly!
